      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>The advisory groups will have ongoing discussions over 2019 on policy, system design and implementation. The groups will meet on a regular basis and explore in detail the contents of the proposals. Members of the advisory groups are required to represent a composite view from their industry and members.</p>

</div>
</div>

      </section>
    </div>

